name: Kanzashi - かんざし
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:

If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

Kanzashi - かんざし

With this exotic LoRA I am taking you to Japan in order to appreciate the culture of Kanzashi.

Kanzashi are traditionally made by hand. It takes very long to make and requires patience.

Those head decorations are usually worn by geisha and are a staple of traditional Japanese fashion.

Today this ancestral art comes to you in LoRA format!
